{"tid":587920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"票照投但絕不含撚，新東我就算入去寫潮文都唔撚含","createTime":"2018-03-10T19:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T07:15:25.000Z","uid":4036,"like":115,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b602ab401f493d4639bc3fc0b8570cda2db77495","tid":587920,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:42:33.000Z","msg":"我入去寫潮文寫十分鐘<br />\n就有十分鐘時間建制泛民都用唔到我果格投票<br />\n建制？我屌你老母<br />\n泛民？我屌埋你老豆<br />\nD人比人DQ你又唔撚出聲？<br />\n家下又口口聲聲反DQ? 做撚左d咩？<br />\n仲有面目出黎選 厚顏無恥到咁我未見識過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9401c302f4d51d24e65f6abba538637c1598250b","tid":587920,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:53:22.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"ea95339850c0c618b6047a67af8f9f10c04f1655","tid":587920,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd917f5507df5809bdebf93f30cffa859f0a567","tid":587920,"uid":62097,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T20:19:56.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d68395a96cceaae5a945515c279a4d0d713efeb0","tid":587920,"uid":16034,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T20:22:49.000Z","msg":"比著係港島/九西都仲有可能會去含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  范國威？食屎啦屌你老母 我投比娥姐都唔撚會射比佢"},{"pid":"eda8602ebd970804ea314f8416738b6d1567adeb","tid":587920,"uid":39796,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T20:31:43.000Z","msg":"支持廢票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n養新移民養蝻亞難民<br />\n修改議事規則<br />\n白頭佬之禍<br />\n咩關鍵一席楊岳橋<br />\n咩以命抗爭陳志全<br />\n開會唔齊腳<br />\n咩抗命十幾人但無視旺角受罪者<br />\n割蓆<br />\n<br />\n咁多年做過乜嘢..."},{"pid":"9729a446c8840cfb6fa0c0ebf8890da6de6a3349","tid":587